'About this space' Raw Description: Experience a stylish and scenic stay at our one bedroom apartment, on the 21st floor,  at 16 on Bree. With Ocean, Signal Hill and City Views thought, it’s the perfect location for your Cape Town holiday or vacay. We cant wait to welcome you.The spaceWelcome to Royal Reflections. As you enter the apartment you are welcome by style and luxury.  We spend alot of time getting the apartment ready and making sure the apartment offers more than just the perfect spot for your next holiday. The apartment has a full kitchen and lounge and separate room. The bathroom is off the bedroom and the whole apartment is over looking the beautiful ocean, cape town has to offer. We will make sure u have all you need for that perfect holiday.Other things to noteElectricity is not to be misused. Please switch off all appliances when not needed. Heating and aircon must not be misused. If we realise it’s being misused, the additional cost will be for your account. We will notify you if this happens. Thanks so much for your understanding.Camping cots are available for rent during your stay, depending on availability. Please arrange this with us. T’s & C’s apply.NO SMOKING IS ALLOWED. R5000 will be given when security knocks on your door.
